original_title: Valmay the Visitor from Beep Beep Beep Bleetlebox 967
overview: The story of Valmay Beepzup's first night on Earth. After winning the Miss Universe Beauty Pageant on her planet, Valmay is awarded the glory of being sent to Earth as an ambassador. With the assistance of her transmographer she is able to morph into a variety of human forms & so slip seamlessly amongst humans.
title: Valmay the Visitor from Beep Beep Beep Bleetlebox 967
